successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 weeks'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 weeks'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 weeks'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

adjusted adjustments
successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '☔'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '☔'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '☔'
                   
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'

                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri

            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   
              ) > 2
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   
              ) > 3
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 2
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'

                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2

            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'

                SELECT SUM(score)

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   
              ) > 15
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🧑‍🎄'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🧑‍🎄'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🧑‍🎄'
                   
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🧑‍🎄'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🧑‍🎄'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🧑‍🎄'
                   
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🧑‍🎄'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🧑‍🎄'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🧑‍🎄'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '💿'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '💿'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '💿'
                   
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'

          FROM scores AS s1

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '1 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '1 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '1 days'
              ) > 3
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'

          FROM scores AS s1

                FROM scores AS s2

                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 weeks'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

adjusted adjustments
successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '4 weeks'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '4 weeks'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '4 weeks'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '4 weeks'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '4 weeks'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '4 weeks'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '4 weeks'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '4 weeks'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '4 weeks'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 days'AND s2.stamp <= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 days'AND s1.stamp <= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 days'AND s2.stamp <= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 weeks'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 weeks'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 weeks'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '⛰️'

          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '⛰️'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '⛰️'
                   
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 MONTHS'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 MONTHS'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 MONTHS'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 months'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 months'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 months'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 months'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 months'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 months'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

            SELECT SUM(score)

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'

                FROM scores AS s2

                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 weeks'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🔥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '6 weeks'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🔥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '6 weeks'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🔥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '6 weeks'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

adjusted adjustments
successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 weeks'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 weeks'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 weeks'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '6 weeks'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '6 weeks'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '6 weeks'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '6 weeks'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '6 weeks'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '6 weeks'
              ) > 0
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 weeks'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 weeks'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 weeks'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            AND s1.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   AND s2.stamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '14 days'
              ) > 1
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;

successfully queried:  SELECT DISTINCT song_name, spotify_uri, (
            SELECT SUM(score)
            FROM scores AS s2
            WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
              AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
               
          ) AS total_score
          FROM scores AS s1
          WHERE s1.themoji = '🦥'
            
            and (
                SELECT SUM(score)
                FROM scores AS s2
                WHERE s2.spotify_uri = s1.spotify_uri
                  AND s2.themoji = '🦥'
                   
              ) > 4
            ORDER BY total_score DESC;
